    "37302": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Venti",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Oh? What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Though I was just wondering if you would happen to follow me..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to know more about the Anemo God."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "You speak of the God of Anemo, Barbatos? He already disappeared from Mondstadt a long time ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Liyue and Inazuma's respective gods of Geo and Electro are still present, but Mondstadt has seen many a moon since they last saw their own god."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Why do you wish to know about the God of Anemo? Does it have something to do with Dvalin?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh... ahhh... it's because gods..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yes, someone told me about Dvalin's past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Just how is it that everyone sees Stormterror? I'm quite curious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "That said, there's no need to rush..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "I have not been back in a while, it seems there are a few who are unhappy with my arrival."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
