    "37402": {
        "Desc": "See how Venti borrows the Holy Lyre",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Let me handle this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Hello there, Sister."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "May the Anemo God bless you, young bard. How can I help you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Actually, I know a secret that can save Mondstadt from its current predicament."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Oh, what a blessing from the God of Anemo!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "But you should report that to the Knights of Favonius. Why have you come to me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Hahaha, because you, dear sister, are able to help!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "I'd like to borrow... the Holy Lyre. With it, I'll be able to help Stormterror—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Please see yourselves out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "What?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "It's a vicious dragon indeed, but once the Acting Grand Master makes up her mind, nothing can stand in the Knights' way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "That's simply not acceptable. Wouldn't Stormterror end up getting killed that way?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "That foolish beast betrayed the winds. Not even the God of Anemo themselves would forgive it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Wow..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Please, I beg of you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "I'm afraid not, little bard."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "(Strange... Somehow I feel so bad rejecting this sweet child...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Then... I guess I'm left with no other choice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "I cannot hide anymore!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "My disciples, rejoice! Behold, the <color=#00E1FFFF>God of Anemo, Barbatos</color> has descended!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Shocked, aren't you? Don't you just want to cry out and rejoice? How does it feel to finally meet the god you've been serving?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "If there's nothing else, I'll be going back to handle the Cathedral's paperwork now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Wait—"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "37403": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Eh? She didn't even bat an eyelid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "But, I have at least learned what I wanted to know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "She didn't deny that the Cathedral is enshrining the Holy Lyre."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#Now, {NICKNAME}, since you're the hotshot of the Knights of Favonius..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Maybe you can give it a shot."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "37404": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Venti",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Barbatos bless you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hello."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Ah, it's you! The newcomer of the Knights of Favonius, aren't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#I am the Honorary Knight of Favonius, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "I know you. You and Amber saved Mondstadt that day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "So what brings you here? Tasks from the Acting Grand Master?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yes, actually. The Knights of Favonius would like to borrow the Holy Lyre..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Is that so?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Not that I don't trust you. It's just that a suspicious bard came looking to borrow the Holy Lyre as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "He's full of nonsense and even called himself Barbatos. He must be up to something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "There are regulations in place for the use of the Holy Lyre. Currently, it's only used in Ludi Harpastum."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Signed documents from the Grand Master, Seneschal, and Community Representative are all required."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "So, may I see the document from the Knights of Favonius?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Grand Master didn't mention it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm sorry, I forgot to bring it here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon ate it on our way here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "A signed document is required. Without it, there's not much I can do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gotelinde",
                    "T": "Now, if you'll excuse me. I really am quite busy as of late."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
