    "37501": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Venti",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "It didn't work... I knew it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You \"knew it\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#I just wanted to know how influential {NICKNAME} — the hotshot of the Knights of the Favonius — is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "You see, the best warrior should always be presented with the best sword, and yet here we are..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Does the story not make for a fitting ballad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So what are you trying to say? That we're not good enough?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "No, that's not it. More of a commentary regarding Mondstadt's inability to see the warrior standing right before its very eyes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Very well. Looks like borrowing it is not going to be possible. We're simply going to have to steal it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Today we stand for free will! Any suggestions on just how we steal it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Come now, speak up. That's what free will is for."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't want to steal anything!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Hahaha, look at you. Sidetracked from the start."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "But seriously, you're more suitable for the job than I."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Aside from singing, I don't really have any other talents."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Besides, if I was caught, I'd have no one to right the grave injustice of my arrest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How can it be a \"grave injustice\" if you got caught stealing red-handed?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#But things are different for {NICKNAME}. You are the superstar of the Knights of Favonius. You have made contributions to Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Should you get caught, you would easily be able to talk your way out of it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Stop mentioning us getting caught!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}... What do you say?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm sorry— Wait... Did you just say... you're Barbatos?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Ah, yes. Seems I did mention that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Your point being?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If you really are a god, then we can't simply abandon you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Why does your decision hinge upon whether or not I am a god?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Paimon'll fill you in on {NICKNAME}'s background story when we get the time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And if you're not a god, then I'll help Dvalin anyway."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I will bring you the Holy Lyre der Himmel."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't want to see another separation."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
