    "37702": {
        "Desc": "Return to the tavern the following night",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "You're here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "#Wait, you're... {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...Jean?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why is the Acting Grand Master here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Well, first of all, I contacted more than one person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Secondly, she came here as \"Jean\" herself, not as the Acting Grand Master."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "A Jean you would never see, even as an Honorary Knight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "What a surprise."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "I heard about the Holy Lyre, but I never suspected it was you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "So, the sound of the Holy Lyre can purify Stormterror and return it to normal... Is that true?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#That's right! {NICKNAME} is putting themselves on the front line to try and resolve this Stormterror issue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Now that's the hotshot of the Knights of Favonius I'm talking about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Feels like we're breaking the law though..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "I understand this kind of absurd explanation is hard to believe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "But, we can ask the bard to play the song again to try and persuade—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "I believe you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "To persuade our stubborn comman— Wait, what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "I can't think of any reason for Dvalin's betrayal, given it was once one of The Four Winds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "However, if it was poisoned in the battle over Mondstadt all those years ago..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "And then corrupted by the Abyss Mage after it woke up — we can't really blame it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "But as Acting Grand Master I obviously cannot make such a statement publicly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Diplomatic pressure from the Fatui makes it hard for us to seek a peaceful resolution to the Stormterror issue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "People would think I've lost grip on the gravity of the situation. That's why I can only do this in private."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Hmph."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "That's one of the reasons I don't like the Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "What surprises me is that you would believe an outlander so easily..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "#My cautious and meticulous <color=#00E1FFFF>superior</color>, even you trust {M#him}{F#her}. Don't you, sir?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "I already told you not to call me sir... Never mind. We don't often get to work together after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sir?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Pretend to not have heard anything)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! Um... This is really awkward..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "I have a rough idea of where the Holy Lyre der Himmel is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "(Nice recovery! She's really talented at changing the subject...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "The conflict between Mondstadt and Snezhnaya stems from the conflict between the seven nations and their respective gods."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "The Cryo God's Fatui seem to be after the Anemo God's power."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So are they going to take over the defense of Mondstadt?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So they want to kill Dvalin?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "If the Knights of Favonius publicly prevented an attempt on Dvalin's head, then..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "The only other way to affect the Anemo God's power is to take the Holy Lyre."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "The number of Fatui that have come to Mondstadt is far from limited."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "I've already managed to... coerce a few reports out of them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Diluc has determined that the Holy Lyre is not being held in the Goth Grand Hotel."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "I imagine they don't want to leave something stolen in a place where it could be so easily found."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon gets it. If too much of a scene gets made then it becomes a big diplomatic issue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Hmph, such is the diplomacy between the seven nations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Outlander, ready to go?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
