    "37904": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Jean",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "It worked, as expected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "This youthful glow..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Praising yourself? Really?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "...I was talking about the Holy Lyre."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#Thanks to {NICKNAME} having purified the crystal, the Holy Lyre won't continue to lose power."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "That said, its power is far from replenished. It'd be great if we could get more tears."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'll help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How can we gather more?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Right. How do we do that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How can we make Dvalin cry? By hitting him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "I can surmise that Dvalin will already be crying..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Suffering alone in some deserted place..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Dvalin..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Poor baby..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "This is not something that an Honorary Knight can accomplish alone. I will mobilize the rest of the knights to assist."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "#When you get the Teardrop Crystal, please let {NICKNAME} perform the purification process."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Leave it to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Heroes supporting each other and setting out on a journey together... How exciting!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Lemme come up with a song for you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is that all you're going to do? Just sing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Wouldn't be much of a bard if I didn't now, would I?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph. You're so cheeky... You deserve an ugly nickname."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, Paimon knows! From now on, you'll be known as \"<color=#00E1FFFF>Tone-Deaf Bard</color>\"!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
