    "38304": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It worked!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "It seems completely different from before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "The lyre's Anemo power seems fully restored. We should be able to use it now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "#It's all thanks to you, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Now, where should we summon Stormterror?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "It must be away from the city, else there will be casualties should we fail."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Perhaps here at the winery..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "If the winery was destroyed, it's not something I couldn't eventually fix, but... I'd still rather not go through the hassle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "The wind that blows at sea or in high places should be able to carry a bard's words far away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "It's never going to work if the air is too dry or suffocating."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon understands. Sea or high places, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then the best location to play the lyre would be..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A cliff?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Near the sea?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "In the sky? You could play the lyre as you're gliding through the air..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Even Amber would never think of doing such a thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "If you go east from Starfell Lake, there are mountains south of the beach."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..Oh! You mean that beach you were snoring away on and Paimon had to wake you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "If you head to where the cliff juts out — that place is known as <color=#00E1FFFF>Starsnatch Cliff</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "What do you think, bard? Meets the requirements, no?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "Lemme think... Starsnatch Cliff..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Venti",
                    "T": "...Alright, let's do it there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Very well. Then let's meet at Starsnatch Cliff when we are ready."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Please don't be late."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hee-hee! Yes, Ma'am!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Ah, sorry. I didn't mean to..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
